-394888904.text: "We propose that during TNFalpha induced apoptosis, PKCdelta mediated phosphorylation of p21 (WAF1 and CIP1) at (146) Ser attenuates the Cdk2 binding of p21 (WAF1 and CIP1) and thereby upregulates Cdk2 activity."
